    <title>Seam Menus and Actions</title>

    <para>In this chapter we provide a description of Seam actions that are available from</para>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para>Menu bar</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Toolbar</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Context menus in views</para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>


